  "title": "Sales Executive",
  "description": "<h2>Job Description & Requirements</h2><p><strong>Position:</strong> Sales Executive (Motor Insurance)</p><h3>Job Overview</h3><p>As a Sales Executive, you will be responsible for promoting and selling <strong>car and commercial vehicle insurance</strong> products. You will handle customer enquiries, manage policy renewals, and ensure accurate documentation while delivering excellent customer service.</p><h3>Working Location</h3><ul><li><p>6 minutes’ walk from <strong>Somerset MRT Station</strong></p></li></ul><h3>Working Hours</h3><ul><li><p>Monday to Friday</p></li><li><p>9:00 AM – 6:00 PM</p></li></ul><h3>Key Responsibilities</h3><ul><li><p>Achieve and fulfil assigned sales targets</p></li><li><p>Promptly follow up with clients on motor insurance enquiries</p></li><li><p>Handle policy renewals and maintain long-term client relationships</p></li><li><p>Prepare motor insurance quotations and issue policies</p></li><li><p>Process insurance policies and related documentation accurately</p></li><li><p>Update and maintain customer records in the database</p></li><li><p>Provide general administrative support when required</p></li></ul><h3>Requirements</h3><ul><li><p>Strong organisational skills with excellent attention to detail</p></li><li><p>Good written and verbal communication skills</p></li><li><p>Strong interpersonal and customer service skills</p></li><li><p>Ability to work independently and manage multiple tasks in a fast-paced environment</p></li><li><p>Results-driven with a service-oriented mindset</p></li><li><p>Proactive, responsible, and able to work efficiently under pressure</p></li></ul><p></p>",
